/* ProfileSettingsView — Privacy & Safety */
"Control what this browser can access and share" = "Controle a qu\U00E9 puede acceder y compartir este navegador";
"Shared Clipboard" = "Portapapeles compartido";
"Copy and paste text and images between your Mac and this browser. When turned off, the browser\U2019s clipboard is completely isolated." = "Copie y pegue texto e im\U00E1genes entre su Mac y este navegador. Cuando est\U00E1 desactivado, el portapapeles del navegador queda completamente aislado.";
